e une nouvelle et alléchante perspective du monde dans lequel nous vivons.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Feb 2021) 0aGame theory. 4aHistory of science. 4aMathematics. 7aSCIENCE / History.2bisacsh1 aPastine, Tuvana, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759822447423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9782759822447.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK